messages.text: Yes. Maybe I’m a night owl.
Whoever this is, it’s not funny.
I’m mean, I’m scared like you.
How do u know about that?
How do you know I’ve seen him?
I know. I tracked you down using the URL.
Are you a hacker or something?
Not much to do at night when ur not sleeping :).
How do I know you’ve actually seen him?
U read my blog. U would already know what he looks like.
Tell me the only thing that can make him go away.
And when u turn it off?
A few hours between when the sun comes up and school starts. You?
I wear a face mask and keep all the lights on.
But lately I haven’t slept much.
Do you think there are others like us?
Your the only other person I know of.
Have you ever turned the lights off and pretended to be asleep.
I can hear him creeping toward me.
He gets close and I can feel his breath. It’s cold.
But then I freak out and turn on the light.
What if he wants to tell us something?
What if he wants to kill us?
I think we should work together.
Maybe we can help each other.
I’ve tried recording him with my laptop. I can see him on the live feed. But he never shows up on the recording.
I can hack into your laptop and watch you while you’re sleeping.
Hear me out. I’ll watch him while you sleep and see what he does.
You can plug your lamp into a remote that I can access from the web.
If he does anything dangerous, I’ll turn on the lamp and he’ll disappear.
U can do the same for me.
Yes. I can walk u through it. That way we’ll be like each other’s guardian angels.
We just have to sleep at different times.
I am too. But maybe we can figure out what he wants.
Ted. Good to meet you Abby.
The lamp took a second to turn on.
His face was so close to yours.
It looked like maybe he was whispering something.
I think I had a dream that I was cold.
Do remember any words? Something he said?
We have to find out what he wants.
I can’t go on like this.
I’m going to lose my apartment.
I’ve even stayed at friend’s houses.
I know. I know. That’s why we have to figure this out.
What if you turn out the light and pretend to be asleep?
That way we can remember what he says.
Otherwise, this could be the rest of our lives.
Lie back down on the side closest to him.
I’ll turn it on again if he gets too close.
I can feel it. He’s cold.
Like u said we can’t go on like this.
I remember what he said to me.
He said I only need one.
